{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"optional","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"voipDidCancelCall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"voipMessage","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"PWVoIPMessage","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshVoIP\/documentation\/PushwooshVoIP\/PWVoIPMessage","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@PushwooshVoIP@objc(cs)PWVoIPMessage"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The VoIP message containing call information. Use "},{"code":"voipMessage.callId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to identify which call was cancelled."}]}],"name":"voipMessage"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is invoked when the remote party cancels their outgoing call before the local user has a chance to answer.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The SDK automatically dismisses the CallKit incoming call UI when this occurs.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"To enable call cancellation, include these fields in your VoIP push payload:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"callId","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" - A unique server-provided identifier for the call"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancelCall"},{"text":" - Set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":" for cancellation requests"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text